# ImageAI — .raginclude for RAG knowledge base
# Generated: 2026-02-27
# Stack: Python desktop application (open-source AI image/video generation)
#
# ImageAI is open-source. All committed documentation is intentionally public
# and meant to educate developers about workflows, architecture decisions,
# code reviews, and implementation patterns.
#
# Rule: if it's not in .gitignore, it's fair game for RAG indexing.
# *.log files are gitignored and excluded; all other markdown is included.

# All root-level markdown docs (README, CHANGELOG, CLAUDE.md, GEMINI.md,
# AGENTS.md, MIDI_KARAOKE_FEATURES, OLLAMA_SETUP, HF guides, prompt libs, etc.)
*.md

# All documentation (features, FAQ, user guides, code reviews,
# implementation notes, LLM contracts, reference image docs, etc.)
Docs/**/*.md

# Stack context
requirements.txt
